data.description: Medieval castle door meets techy design in this awesome 5 bed/4 bath smart home, located in Cheney school district. Kitchen is full of upgrades - black quartz countertops with stone backsplash, alder cabinets, and smart core waterproof flooring AS WELL AS all new appliances in 2019: induction stovetop, convection microwave, black stainless steel smart fridge, smart oven, and touch free faucet. Main floor primary bedroom has a full en suite and a walk-in closet with a custom built-in closet organizer. Move upstairs to find 4 more bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a large family room. Vinyl fencing fully encloses the backyard to provide privacy & a great space for pets. 240amp/50v wiring in the garage allows for electric car charging. Other smart features include: a smart thermostat, smart door lock, 1 gig internet, ethernet drops in all of the bedrooms (8 total), and a smart sprinkler system that monitors the weather and adjusts watering for you! Ask your agent about the 3D tour!!
